夠錢個陣d女就自然會埋身<br />\n咁你應該會開心好多</blockquote><br />\n但有時會覺得 去到真係有成就先埋你身既女根本唔係真心<br />\n當然大前提係你有成就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 我都係想趁讀緊書 有另一半一齊陪你溫習 一齊返學放學 班房門口接對方呢啲姐<br />\n中學試唔到 唔想大專都冇<br />\n廿尾三十既時候 下下都講錢 冇乜意思<br />\n諗起果篇IT毒撚一生既潮文<br />\n講得幾岩 我感覺步緊佢後塵"},{"pid":"6515840e5201feb0e49f3053ce0751baf01d2167","tid":464870,"uid":60064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女呢啲，係主動聊佢地，表現得風趣幽默啲，引到佢地笑就得喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連對象都冇可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n異性朋友唔係冇 不過係一句起兩句止果啲<br />\n對佢地0興趣"},{"pid":"729b1df0f912d6cb99a5cdae7fbffd0017c1ff2f","tid":464870,"uid":60064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2257d572a2aff08c760445e0173ffeccb7dd41","tid":464870,"uid":60064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"估唔到上嚟連登都要單機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c96748d4d8082b6628c3b4981d94afd29c34544","tid":464870,"uid":19906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>估唔到上嚟連登都要單機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有我"},{"pid":"f404b053327e0a267110d570add29364516ed02e","tid":464870,"uid":60064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:45:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>估唔到上嚟連登都要單機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有我</blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d055617a78a843efcf8f4505a3b2b7b25c4ca88b","tid":464870,"uid":19906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:49:36.000Z","msg":"分手第3日<br />\n而家自虐mode<br />\n愈來愈頹"},{"pid"